2008-03-16 10:33  danmc

	* src/: find.c, parse_y.y: Only use the min annular ring parameter
	  for checking the annular rings on pins and vias.  Previously the
	  minimum copper width setting was also used.  Changed after a
	  discussion on geda-user.  Also make sure we use the minimum
	  copper width as the default if the .pcb file doesn't specify the
	  minimum annulus.

